```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "fastmail-test": {
      "type": "http",
      "url": "http://localhost:3000",
      "headers": {
        "Authorization": "Bearer <your-fastmail-api-token>"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Replace `<your-fastmail-api-token>` with your Fastmail API token. Want me to update the file for you?

